module.exports = /*#__PURE__*/JSON.parse('[{"id":"r1","productId":"p1","author":"Jordan M.","location":"London, UK","rating":5,"title":"Exactly what streetwear should be","body":"This tee hits different. The weight is perfect — not flimsy, not stiff. Oversized fit is on point without looking sloppy. Wore it to a show last week and got three compliments. Already ordered another colour.","date":"2026-03-12","verified":true,"size":"L","color":"Black"},{"id":"r2","productId":"p1","author":"Kai T.","location":"Manchester, UK","rating":5,"title":"Premium quality, no cap","body":"Didn\'t expect this level of quality at this price. Fabric is thick and structured. Washed it twice and it hasn\'t shrunk or faded. The boxy cut is exactly as shown. Will be back.","date":"2026-03-28","verified":true,"size":"XL","color":"White"},{"id":"r3","productId":"p1","author":"Asha R.","location":"Birmingham, UK","rating":4,"title":"Great tee, sizing runs slightly big","body":"Love the quality and the look. Just be aware the sizing runs a touch bigger than expected — I usually wear M but an S would have worked. Still keeping it though, the oversized look is intentional anyway.","date":"2026-04-01","verified":true,"size":"M","color":"Black"},{"id":"r4","productId":"p2","author":"Luca V.","location":"Bristol, UK","rating":5,"title":"Best hoodie I\'ve bought this year","body":"Heavyweight, structured, and the fit is immaculate. The colour hasn\'t faded at all. Warm enough for UK winters but not too bulky. I\'ve been wearing this on repeat.","date":"2026-02-18","verified":true,"size":"L","color":"Black"},{"id":"r5","productId":"p2","author":"Sam W.","location":"Leeds, UK","rating":5,"title":"Honestly exceeded expectations","body":"Was sceptical ordering from a new brand but DEKKRY delivered. The hoodie is thick, the stitching is clean, no loose threads. Customer service was quick too when I had a question about sizing.","date":"2026-03-05","verified":true,"size":"XL","color":"Grey"},{"id":"r6","productId":"p2","author":"Priya K.","location":"London, UK","rating":4,"title":"Solid hoodie, fast delivery","body":"Really happy with this. The grey colourway is a perfect neutral — goes with everything. Delivery was super fast too. Taking off one star only because the pocket lining could be thicker.","date":"2026-03-20","verified":true,"size":"M","color":"Grey"},{"id":"r7","productId":"p3","author":"Tyler B.","location":"Glasgow, UK","rating":5,"title":"These cargos are it","body":"Fit, fabric, details — everything is on point. The pockets are actually functional and the taper is perfect. Not too baggy, not too slim. Styled them with the DEKKRY tee and the fit was fire.","date":"2026-03-10","verified":true,"size":"32","color":"Black"},{"id":"r8","productId":"p3","author":"Nadia A.","location":"London, UK","rating":5,"title":"Finally a cargo that fits right","body":"I\'ve tried a lot of cargos and these are the best fit I\'ve found. The waistband is comfortable and the taper sits exactly right. Already ordered in khaki too.","date":"2026-03-25","verified":true,"size":"30","color":"Olive"},{"id":"r9","productId":"p4","author":"Marcus J.","location":"Nottingham, UK","rating":5,"title":"Statement piece, actually wearable","body":"Loads of jackets claim to be statement pieces but they never work in practice. This one actually does. Clean enough to dress up, bold enough to stand out. Quality is excellent.","date":"2026-02-28","verified":true,"size":"L","color":"Black"},{"id":"r10","productId":"p4","author":"Elena S.","location":"London, UK","rating":4,"title":"Great quality, runs a bit small","body":"Love the jacket. The material feels premium and the cut is clean. Only thing — size up. I\'m usually an M and the L fits perfectly. Once you get the sizing right it\'s a 5-star piece.","date":"2026-03-15","verified":true,"size":"L","color":"Black"},{"id":"r11","productId":"p5","author":"Demi O.","location":"Edinburgh, UK","rating":5,"title":"The joggers I\'ve been looking for","body":"Soft, structured, and they actually hold their shape after washing. The fit is athletic but relaxed — perfect for the gym or just out. Bought two pairs.","date":"2026-03-08","verified":true,"size":"M","color":"Black"},{"id":"r12","productId":"p5","author":"Finn C.","location":"Cardiff, UK","rating":5,"title":"Comfort + style, rare combo","body":"These are genuinely the most comfortable joggers I own but they don\'t look like lazy wear. The fit is tailored enough to wear out. Material is thick and doesn\'t pill.","date":"2026-04-02","verified":true,"size":"L","color":"Grey"},{"id":"r13","productId":"p6","author":"Zayn M.","location":"London, UK","rating":5,"title":"Clean graphic, quality print","body":"Graphic tees are hit or miss but this one is clean. The print hasn\'t cracked after multiple washes, the fit is great, and the graphic is subtle enough to pair with anything.","date":"2026-02-20","verified":true,"size":"L","color":"Black"},{"id":"r14","productId":"p7","author":"Rosa T.","location":"Liverpool, UK","rating":4,"title":"Great shorts for summer","body":"Really happy with these. The length is perfect — not too long, not too short. Fabric is a nice mid-weight. Would give 5 stars if the waistband drawstring was slightly longer.","date":"2026-03-30","verified":true,"size":"M","color":"Black"},{"id":"r15","productId":"p8","author":"Chris N.","location":"Sheffield, UK","rating":5,"title":"Vest that actually fits well","body":"Finally a vest with a proper fit — not too wide, not too tight. The fabric has a nice weight to it. Wearing it layered over the hoodie and it looks great.","date":"2026-04-03","verified":true,"size":"L","color":"Black"}]');

